# AKOS Documentation-Config Sync

When modifying files matched by the globs above, check whether documentation
needs a corresponding update. These contracts are ordered by trigger.

## Sync Contracts

### Config changes

| Trigger file | Docs to update | Section / area |
|:-------------|:---------------|:---------------|
| `config/model-catalog.json` | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | "Model Catalog" section |
| `config/model-catalog.json` | `docs/USER_GUIDE.md` | RunPod / GPU deployment sections |
| `config/model-tiers.json` | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | "Model Tier Registry" table |
| `config/environments/*.env.example` | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | "Environment Profiles" section |
| `config/environments/*.json` | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | "Dual-Mode RunPod Architecture", env overlay tables |
| `config/openclaw.json.example` | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | "Multi-Provider Configuration", agent registry |
| `config/agent-capabilities.json` | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | "Role-Safe Capability Enforcement" |
| `config/mcporter.json.example` | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | "MCP Server Topology" |
| `config/workspace-scaffold/**` | `config/workspace-scaffold/README.md` | Scaffold structure description |

